    "sextile": "Solar-return Moon sextile natal Moon: an emotionally comfortable, gentle year. Your feelings are in accord with you; comfort and support come easily. Strength: emotional balance and warm bonds; the risk, comfortable passivity.",
    "square": "Solar-return Moon square natal Moon: a year of emotional tension and ups and downs. Old habits and new needs rub; restlessness and unsettledness are possible. Strength: growth in emotional maturity; the risk, moodiness, anxiety, and wavering.",
    "trine": "Solar-return Moon trine natal Moon: a warm, cozy year in tune with your own feelings. Emotions flow easily; home and loved ones give support. Strength: emotional harmony and care; the risk, overly cozy passivity.",
